                <note>2.1 Serinus hortulanus 2.2] <hi rend="italic">underl blue crayon</hi></note>
                <note>2.2 (Girlitz)] ‘in Bechstein Fringilla serinus Linn.’<ref target="#foot.f5"/> <hi rend="italic">added ink</hi></note>
                <note>2.2 Dryospiza canaria] <hi rend="italic">underl blue crayon</hi></note>
